channel.title: I cant control my server! * Part 2 of My server wont run....*
channel.description:
Ok I fixed most things...
I can make myself admin now. I can update my stats now. I can make mods ect...
Things I still need fixed are....
I Can't spawn now. (I think I need to put a code somewhere to get spawning or something)???
I have a no ip thing. But I still have a question....
The question is.. Lets say I have like 4 sources downloaded.... How do I give my No-Ip to one of the sources.. Like lets say I port forward it. And I use the no-ip for people to get onto my server.. How do I know what one the no-ip works for?
And on my no-Ip thing.. The ______.no-ip.biz has a face blushing next to it...... Whats that mean?
Please help with that!!!

item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

Anyways the playerRights problem.

Search:

out.write(playerRights);

Replace That With This:

if (playerRights == 3) { out.write(2); //Crown fixup } else { out.write(playerRights); // mod level }

Close client.java, save, now open it again;

Search:

//start of moderator/admin list, 1 = mod, 2 = staff, 3 = admin

Scroll down till you see, if(playerName.equalsIgnoreCase("

Replace Whatever is between the " " With your name.

Close, save, compile, and run.

Anyone want to help me… I really need help with this…[br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 30, 2007, 06:11:33 PM[/size][hr]Here is a way more detailed explination of what my problem is here…

I have my own server.
I can train the skills in the server and they will stay that level.
The logs will show when I log in, Will log my stats.

But…

If I try to update my stats and make them all 99.
It wont show up as that in game.

If I try to make myself Mod/Admin/Owner…
It wont show up like that in game and I wont have admin/mod/owner powers either…

I cant spawn…

Anyone please help?

And also I need help port forwarding… The tuts for it didn’t help me…

I have this type of router…

It says this on the router at least…

Network Everywhere
Cable/DSL
4 port router
LINKSYS
Model NR041

Idk if that helpped any. But I need help Port Forwarding.

Also I noticed before someone said that if on your No-Ip the smiley face is blushing like has pink cheecks something was wrong…??

Mine has that… If anyone knows about that too help would be appreciated!

Please somebody help me
